Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  我來幫她換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才愛理來電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說已經聯繫上了學姐的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻乃去休息吧  剩下的事交給我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太勉強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽學姐  你太勉強自己了
